he waveform monitor screen can be picture-in-picture on top the  video image and the overlay picture can be placed in any of the screen\'s  four corners.                                         </dd></dl></p>',1,NULL,6,0,'','250','750','2250',324,'Monitors','Monitors',0),(325,'<p>The BT-LH80W 16:9 HD/SD LCD monitor is a versatile solution for studio and field monitoring. <br /><br />&#13;\rThe compact 7.9\" multi-format LCD monitor features advanced video processing technology and delivers high-resolution (800 x 450 pixel) playback and production-quality performance with advanced focus assists for critical focusing in HD. <br /><br />&#13;\rThis compact, low-power unit can double as an electronic viewfinder for use with Panasonic high definition camcorders</p>&#13;\r<ul><li>The LH80W is ideal for use in dual rack mounts and mobile vehicles.</li>&#13;\r    <li>Focus Assistance includes a Focus-in-Red function (the outlines turn red when sharp focus is achieved) and a Pixel-to-Pixel 2.4X function (to help sharpen focus)</li>&#13;\r    <li>Advanced video processor ensures industry\'s lowest delay</li>&#13;\r    <li>Lightweight design allows for easy on-camera mounting, especially with optional BT-MOUNT</li>&#13;\r    <li>15-pin viewfinder terminal can connect to the 20-pin viewfinder connection on select Panasonic high definition camcorders</li>&#13;\r    <li>Can be powered from select Panasonic high definition camcorders 3 (12V, 1.5 Amps)</li>&#13;\r    <li>800 x 480 pixel WVGA resolution panel (effective 800 x 450)</li>&#13;\r    <li>Simple Cross Hatch overlay function allows users to check camera tilt and composition</li>&#13;\r    <li>Waveform Monitoring, Blue Only and Marker</li>&#13;\r    <li>Displays 4:3 aspect ratio images</li>&#13;\r    <li>RS-232C and GPI remote control terminals</li>&#13;\r    <li>Tally (Front: Red/Green, Back Tally: Red)</li>&#13;\r</ul>','<p>The BT-LH80W 16:9 HD/SD LCD monitor is a versatile solution for studio and field monitoring. <br />